Majority Element:

Link : https://leetcode.com/problems/majority-element/description/

Implementation: (Brute Force)

class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
        int n=nums.length;
        for(int val:nums){
            int c=0;
            for(int el : nums){
                if(el==val){
                    c++;
                }
            }
            if(c>n/2){
            return val;
           }
        }
        return -1;
    }
}

Time Complexity: O(n^2)
Space Complexity: O(1)

