Method - 2 (sorting):

 class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
       Arrays.sort(nums);
       int n=nums.length;
        int freq=0;
       for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
        freq++;
        if(freq>n/2){
            return nums[i];
        }  
       }
       return -1;
    }
}


Time complexity : O(nlogn)
Space Complexity : O(1)

