Optimal Version (Moors Voting Algorithm)


class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
       int freq=0;
       int ans=0;
       for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
        if(freq==0){
            ans=nums[i];
        }
        if(ans==nums[i]){
            freq++;
        }
        else{
            freq--;
         }
       }
       return ans;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
